{"tid":1464074,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁義士見到大家被人玩心戰 你哋對得住佢嗎？","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T21:15:14.000Z","uid":194573,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd15d6b322990c2c733c8440772687f2be6aa906","tid":1464074,"uid":194573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"港共明顯又玩捉鬼 玩心戰<br />\n人民鬥人民 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住<br />\n我哋都唔可以咁善忘<br />\n記住612初心不變<br />\n而家係不分化 不割席 不篤灰遇到最大挑戰<br />\n仲有如何be air都係問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁義士係我哋嘅精神領袖<br />\n所有民意根源都係來自612嘅初心<br />\n咁所有嘢我地都變得出師有名<br />\n我哋都唔可以咁善忘<br />\n<br />\n今晚邊個動搖咗 想捉鬼 被分化<br />\n我罰你去PP跪返一個鐘</span></span>"},{"pid":"35bc31db32e1f7c7077074a5bb393a4ae6e86d8a","tid":1464074,"uid":194573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"69 612 616<br />\n係乜嘢支持你走到今時今日？"},{"pid":"7d2de2a1a762a9f22c9e25eb2841d36d95bc6466","tid":1464074,"uid":68471,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"ad0fe02ce4a2d9a1a3ceda6cdd6d566a8294fb4d","tid":1464074,"uid":194573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"係反暴政<br />\n抑或反內鬼"},{"pid":"0cfb6607baba619f7c7d46202d6ec810dfb1e808","tid":1464074,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"69 612 勿忘初衷<br />\n<br />\n唔好互屌分化啊"},{"pid":"98677cfbc9209db03bb0edd30c688273a4df8312","tid":1464074,"uid":194573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求包唔包括捉內鬼？<br />\n無呀！"},{"pid":"e56c79